Improvements to entity metadata and I/O: - Fix entities not being removed because their id was unset. - Metadata changes system improved, players see their own metadata. - On-fire status is now reflected in entity metadata. - Nicer metadata bitflag manipulation and constants. - Catch more exceptions in entity load/save. - Use a reasonable default when setting GlowItems to null stacks.

Fixed arm swing animation and not being able to fly if Creative is default.

Various network and usability fixes: - Placing items with data (logs, wool) no longer removes the data. - Trying to send messages in Handshake now uses same error as other protocols. - Write timeout pings are only sent in Play. - Closed channel and broken pipe errors are quieter. - Log rotation happens before a record is shown and logs aren't colorized.
A couple of bugfixes to block placement: - Fixed an NPE in BlockPlacementHandler if client tries to place against air. - Fixed GlowChunk not correctly creating new ChunkSections.
Some fixups to RegionFile to fix wildly incorrect structure on Linux. Chunks still sometimes broken.

Improved command handling: - Removed unused command classes and server methods. - Fixed duplicate command not found messages. - Wrap chat on newline characters. - Use results of CommandPreprocessEvent.

Cleanup and fixes to networking: - Tidied logging and error messages - Handle disconnects properly - Tidied JsonMessage hierarchy - Improved HandshakeHandler ordering - Added slf4j-jdk dependency for flow loggers - Handle invalid opcodes, messages, handlers more cleanly
